      "writtenOn": "2021-02-25T18:58:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "the usual risks due to concurrency and non-atomicity.\n\nThe reason I mention risk here is that that dsset.Set is meant to provide atomic deletion of N items from the set as part of another transaction, but it requires using BeginPop().",
