      "message": "Well, both.\n\nFirst consider 2 things:\n1. Eventbox says \"you can consume events transactionally with updating your own DS entities\".\n2. dsset is a helper for eventbox.\n\nNow, back to your question -- eventbox user already can consume events transactionally. So, yes, no need for transaction, and this is faster \u0026 simpler.",
